 today.&quot;}},&quot;i&quot;:0}}]}\" id=\"mwJg\"><span about=\"#mwt9\">\n</span><div class=\"banner-image js-proportonal-resize notheme\" about=\"#mwt9\" id=\"mwJw\" style=\"font-size: 108%;\">\n\t<p><span class=\"mw-default-size nolink interactiveIcon\" typeof=\"mw:File/Frameless\"><span><img resource=\"//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/File:Interactive_icon.svg\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e6/Interactive_icon.svg/250px-Interactive_icon.svg.png\" decoding=\"async\" data-file-width=\"133\" data-file-height=\"200\" data-file-type=\"drawing\" height=\"376\" width=\"250\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e6/Interactive_icon.svg/500px-Interactive_icon.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e6/Interactive_icon.svg/500px-Interactive_icon.svg.png 2x\" class=\"mw-file-element\"></span></span></p>\n\t<div class=\"mainpage-shadowbox notheme banner-box-2 banner-box-left\" style=\"width:45%\">\n        <div style=\"position:relative; float:right; margin:-4px;\">\n        <span typeof=\"mw:File/Frameless\"><a href=\"//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/Previously_Off_the_beaten_path\" title=\"Previously Off the beaten path\"><img alt=\"OtBP\" resource=\"//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/File:Right_turn_icon_white.svg\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8d/Right_turn_icon_white.svg/40px-Right_turn_icon_white.svg.png\" decoding=\"async\" data-file-width=\"20\" data-file-height=\"20\" data-file-type=\"drawing\" height=\"32\" width=\"32\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8d/Right_turn_icon_white.svg/60px-Right_turn_icon_white.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8d/Right_turn_icon_white.svg/120px-Right_turn_icon_white.svg.png 2x\" class=\"mw-file-element\"></a></span></div>\n\t\t<section data-mw-section-id=\"-1\" id=\"mwKA\" aria-labelledby=\"Off_the_Beaten_Path\"><h2 style=\"font-size:1.25em;\" id=\"Off_the_Beaten_Path\" class=\"mw-html-heading\"><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/Previously_Off_the_beaten_path\" title=\"Previously Off the beaten path\">Off the Beaten Path</a></h2>\n        <section data-mw-section-id=\"-1\" id=\"mwKQ\" aria-labelledby=\"Erice\"><h3 style=\"font-size:2em;\" id=\"Erice\" class=\"mw-html-heading\"><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/Erice\" title=\"Erice\">Erice</a></h3>\n\t\t<div class=\"quote\"><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/Erice\" title=\"Erice\">Floating above the clouds on Sicily’s western coast, Erice has been a place of pilgrimage for millennia — from an ancient Temple of Venus to the medieval churches that remain open today.</a></div>\n\t</section></section></div>\n\t<p><span class=\"nolink\" typeof=\"mw:File/Frameless\" data-mw=\"{&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;Erice&quot;}\"><span title=\"Erice\"><img alt=\"Erice\" resource=\"//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/File:OtBT-Erice-bannerA.png\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikivoyage/en/thumb/3/39/OtBT-Erice-bannerA.png/1920px-OtBT-Erice-bannerA.png\" decoding=\"async\" data-file-width=\"3034\" data-file-height=\"1010\" data-file-type=\"bitmap\" height=\"566\" width=\"1700\" class=\"mw-file-element\"></span></span>\n\t<span typeof=\"mw:File/Frameless\" data-mw=\"{&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;Erice&quot;}\"><a href=\"//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/Erice\" title=\"Erice\"><img alt=\"Erice\" resource=\"//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/File:OtBT-Erice-bannerA.png\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikivoyage/en/thumb/3/39/OtBT-Erice-bannerA.png/1920px-OtBT-Erice-bannerA.png\" decoding=\"async\" data-file-width=\"3034\" data-file-height=\"1010\" data-file-type=\"bitmap\" height=\"566\" width=\"1700\" class=\"mw-file-element\"></a></span></p>\n</div>","link":"https://en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/Previously_Off_the_beaten_path","retrieved":1761269123153},{"title":"Featured Travel Topic (Wikivoyage recommendations)","contents":"<link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r4523569\" about=\"#mwt11